latestPosts.caption:
Happy Ending, Adios sbsc 🕊️ 
Big W for page like sbsc meme.
Thank you everyone for always supporting, encouraging, and engaging with the page. I believe 
it brings a smile to your faces sometimes.
Special thanks to Principal Sir for always keeping me in mind during speeches and publicly appreciating, and resolving issues raised through memes, and taking memes with maturity and in a fun way instead of getting offended. XD
Thank you sbsc.
